title: SuperTux Keenish Things
content:
There is this game called "Super Tux" originally developed for Ubuntu (Can be run on Windows 2000+) that is immensely popular on that OS. I've found two things so far that seem to resemble keen, although not intentional, probably.

[img]http://i91.photobucket.com/albums/k296/Medevila/supertuxmushroom.jpg[/img]
This one, actually turns whichever way you are turned, and bounces! Reminds me a lot of the mushroom.

Also, there is a dopefish (looks exactly like it) chasing a little orange fish. They are both both frozen in ice, though. I hope to get a picture of that in soon. Version 3 doesn't have that tile. I need to download an earlier for a bit.
